                     <interp inst="t18220911-42-person417" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am clerk to Messrs. Marsh and Co. bankers in Berner's-street. I cannot say whether I received a Bank post bill from Debenham. The entry of 100 l. 2 s. 11 d. in his book is my writing; the money was put in a drawer, after being twisted up all together; it was then taken away by Mr. Lloyd and entered.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220911-42-person418">
