                     <interp inst="t18220911-42-person425" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at No. 9, Manchester Buildings. The prisoner came to my house in May, and left on a Sunday evening in the same month, saying he had a friend ill in the country, whom he wished to see. He paid me very regular, and always conducted himself exceeding well.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220911-42-person426">
                  JOSEPH 
                  JARMAN
               <interp inst="t18220911-42-person426" type="surname" value="JARMAN"></interp>
